{
  "stem": "17625.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Henry Fuchs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "H-E-N-R-Y and name Fuchs, F-U-C-H-S.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hesiek.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "H-E-S-I-E-K.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tauber.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "T-A-U-B-E-R.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- after my mother's name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was married to my father, Fuchsbrunner, by a rabbi, [INAUDIBLE], without registering to the-- to the-- to the-- with the registry.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So actually, this was a-- in great part, in our town, this was the custom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why, officially, my name is Tauber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But everybody knows me as Fuchsbrunner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fuchsbrunner.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here, I write it F-U-C-H-S-B-R-U-N-N-E-R.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in some places, it was written without N-N-E-R but with a M-E-R.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fuchsbrumer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some other, from the same family, write with an N, Fuchsbruner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it's-- that's was the-- that's the story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "July 8, 1917.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I go here as 1919.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Chrzanów, Galicia, Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "C-H-R-Z-A-N-O-W, O with a-- with a stripe, which means Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was born [SIGHS] in Oklusz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shall I spell it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "O-L-K-U-S-Z.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very near.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was-- this was-- I was Galicia, and he was Congress Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he moved to-- he didn't move, but he-- he came to Chrzanow at a time, by 1905, there was the Russian-Japanese war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, [SIGHS] people who didn't want to serve in the army, they looked for a way to-- for some place where to come.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he changed his address, and he came to Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Chrzanow, he had-- he had family in Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His family, his name was-- Tausowitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Tausowitz was-- Johann Tausowitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was-- he was a veterinarian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And his wife, her name was [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Koshitsky ?] My father's mother's name is [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Koshitsky ?] So actually, it was family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is the reason they came to Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he met my mother there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they got married there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I should give you a good answer. i don't have it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
